<HEADLINE> Bangladesh to Hold Polls in Seven Municipalities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, April 11 (Xinhua) -- Elections to seven municipalities
in Bangladesh will be held on Monday, a press release of the
Election Commission said Sunday.
