<P>
"China will continue to refine its laws and regulations
concerning foreign economic cooperation and trade to strengthen
the protection of the legitimate rights of overseas investors in
accordance with law," said the minister. "The Chinese Government
intends to create an investment environment that is fair,
transparent, in good order, is competitive and is guaranteed by
relevant laws."
</P>
